extendedInfo.description: **ATTENTION**This is a pack for RingPack. Search "RingPack" in the market.You must open the pack at least once to install (even if just updating).*************This is a collection of sounds from The Legend of Zelda: Ocarina of Time. It has samples of:-Adult Link-Young Link-Menu's-Misc EffectsCredit goes to: The Big N & HelpTheWretched.To install, download, and open. It will automatically install and open RingPack.You are free to delete the pack once installed if you wish to clean up your launcher or save application space. It will remain with RingPack until you manually delete it by longpressing the pack's name in RingPack.
